arStrings.szText:
Casting a {c_important}Subterfuge{/c} Skill also spawns an enemy {c_important}Shade Totem{/c} for {c_random}[Affix_Value_1|1|]{/c} seconds. Any damage it takes is replicated onto surrounding enemies at {c_number}[Affix_Value_2]%{/c} effectiveness. 

You may only have {c_number}[Affix."Static Value 0"]{/c} {c_important}Shade Totems{/c} active at a time. This damage counts as a {c_important}Trap{/c} skill.
